OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FA Birmingham City striker has been
OL,8,Ffined more than #16,000 after causing
OL,9,Fa serious three-car crash while over
OL,10,Fthe drink-drive limit.
OL,12,FMarvin Ducksch was told he was lucky
OL,13,Fhe had not killed himself and two
OL,14,Ffemale drivers in the late-night crash
OL,15,Fand he was ordered to pay the victims
OL,16,F#1,000 each in compensation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
