FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FLeamington Spa Magistrates' Court
OL,8,Fheard Ducksch stopped at the scene and
OL,9,Fchecked on the other motorists, one of
OL,10,Fwhom had a nosebleed and injuries to
OL,11,Fher forehead and thumb.
OL,13,FThe 32-year-old pleaded guilty on
OL,14,FWednesday to driving his Mercedes with
OL,15,Fexcess alcohol, namely 53mcg of
OL,16,Falcohol in 100ml of breath, above the
OL,17,Flegal limit of 35mcg.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FMagistrates were told the charge
OL,8,Frelated to a collision on the A3400
OL,9,Fnear Henley-in-Arden in Warwickshire
OL,10,Fat around 10.30pm on Easter Monday.
OL,12,FThe crash happened hours after Ducksch
OL,13,Fappeared as a substitute in
OL,14,FBirmingham's 2-1 defeat to Ispwich
OL,15,FTown at Portman Road.
OL,17,FProsecutor Lina Akther told the court:
OL,18,F"The defendant identified himself to
OL,19,Fthe officers and confirmed he was
OL,20,Finvolved in the collision.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"The defendant stated to the officers
OL,8,Fthat he was driving and he went to
OL,9,Fchange his music and crashed and he
OL,10,Fwasn't sure how."
OL,12,FDucksh, who also claimed to have been
OL,13,Favoiding a tree branch in the road,
OL,14,Fwas arrested and breath tested.
OL,16,FDucksh is currently at Birmingham City
OL,17,Fon a three year deal and has played
OL,18,Ftwice for the senior Germany national
OL,19,Fteam.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FIn a prepared statement to police,
OL,8,FDucksch told the court that he was
OL,9,Fdriving home and admitted "he did have
OL,10,Falcohol before he drove" and had
OL,11,F"clipped an oncoming car and another
OL,12,Fone following behind".
OL,14,FMs Akther said: "He thought he would
OL,15,Fbe under the limit and the defendant
OL,16,Fwas apologetic in his prepared
OL,17,Fstatement."
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@XO]sD@AOUtD@UO]vD@QOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FMagistrates handed Ducksch a 14-month
OL,8,Fdriving ban alongside a fine of
OL,9,F#16,155, a total of #2,000 in
OL,10,Fcompensation, a #2,000 surcharge and a
OL,11,Fbill for costs of #85.
OL,13,FThe court agreed to allow Ducksch to
OL,14,Fpay off the total amount of #20,240 at
OL,15,Fa rate of #2,000 per month.
OL,17,FImposing the fines, chairman of the
OL,18,Fbench John Kiely told the footballer,
OL,19,Fwho lives in Solihull: "Thank you very
OL,20,Fmuch for your patience while we have
OL,21,Fbeen talking about this offence.
OL,26,@{D@XOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"We heard that there was an incident
OL,8,Fin which two vehicles were clipped.
OL,10,F"We have looked at the photographs (of
OL,11,Fthe damaged cars).
OL,13,F"You can consider yourself lucky first
OL,14,Fof all that you weren't killed and
OL,15,Fsecondly that the other drivers
OL,16,Fweren't killed.
OL,18,F"That's how serious this matter is."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FDuring mitigation, defence solicitor
OL,8,FJulia Morgan said Ducksch, whose
OL,9,Fformer clubs include Werder Bremen and
OL,10,FBorussia Dortmund, had a promising
OL,11,Fcareer ahead of him.
OL,13,FMs Morgan told the three magistrates
OL,14,Fduring the 20-minute hearing: "It's
OL,15,Fabundantly clear that damage was
OL,16,Fcaused to those vehicles and the lady
OL,17,Fconcerned was injured during the
OL,18,Fcourse of this."
OL,26,@vD@_OUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FDucksch was comprehensively insured
OL,8,Fand the damage would be covered by the
OL,9,Fpolicy, she said.
OL,11,FMs Morgan added: "Mr Ducksch waited at
OL,12,Fthe scene for the police.
OL,14,F"They didn't arrive immediately but he
OL,15,Fwaited and he checked on the welfare
OL,16,Fof the occupants of the other vehicles.
OL,18,F"He is currently a young man who plays
OL,19,Fas a professional footballer for
OL,20,FBirmingham City Football Club.
OL,26,@sD@ROUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779369077
OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"Not only is he going to be subject to
OL,8,Fthe sentence that you impose today `
OL,9,Ffrom a financial point of view he has
OL,10,Falso been penalised by Birmingham City
OL,11,Ffor his actions that night.
OL,13,F"He has been penalised financially and
OL,14,Ffurther by not being permitted to play
OL,15,Fin a number of matches following this
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,F"That illustrates how seriously
OL,19,Fincidents of this nature are taken."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
