OL,3,CBirmingham City striker fined more
OL,4,Cthan #16,000 after causing three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe lawyer continued: "They (the club)
OL,8,Fhave provided references.
OL,10,F"I hope you have had the opportunity
OL,11,Fto see them and read them.
OL,13,F"In essence they talk about a man of
OL,14,Fimpeccable character in his conduct
OL,15,Ftowards his team, his managers and the
OL,16,Fclub itself.
OL,26,@oD@WOUrD@AOUuD@AOU
